cy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2823572c6a0f66295905105443e0baaf5d557790","tid":2252404,"uid":212459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"成日會好焦慮自己又出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313aa1d5dba6e393038e2953591967abf071c5d6","tid":2252404,"uid":221428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"474b677145e62a1726e887609790ef43a606fd4e","tid":2252404,"uid":185222,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"75012d4961c1e5d3e0075a1835a779deb40873c0","tid":2252404,"uid":29523,"like":31,"dislike":5,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人明要忍個粗心大意嘅人係咩感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:59:49.000Z","msg":"我都唔想架 有啲位真係check 10次8次都鬼暗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"係&hellip;仲要d嘢拖勁耐都唔敢交因為想再check多幾次 搞到效率又好低<br />\n但係最慘無論check幾多次都係有野錯果下真係好frustrating <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534e454e024a68bf2d9f755b045e65c9846f7407","tid":2252404,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068f69133ecb96fc83ec4e871f0e4b65a1dd9edd","tid":2252404,"uid":273014,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"例如d文件有野要做/改，我會將要做嘅野逐點寫低，整個類似check list嘅野，然後做好之後對，睇下有冇野漏或者錯，做左就剔一剔，穩陣啲可以對兩次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"個正解冇人理，你班人係咪真係解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166f130bd5244509ba008c6db88040b142d40695","tid":2252404,"uid":125654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"應該問有冇人明你地同事既感受囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都要幫手執屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbfae3029286939bacabdc4d761b7901495e742","